  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.header": "建造交流发电机",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_1": "交流发电机能够将旋转力转化为电能",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_2": "在转子周围放置磁铁",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_3": "交流发电机将会开始产生电压。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_4": "184V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_5": "使用变压器来调整电压。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_6": "您或许可以考虑使用稳压器来进一步调节电压。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.header": "直观理解电力",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_1": "想象一个首尾相连的线路。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_10": "对于灯泡来说，点的运动会使灯丝升温至白炽化而发光。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_11": "请注意输入的点的数量等于输出的点的数量。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_12": "这就是基尔霍夫电流定律。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_2": "在这条线上放置一些点，把它们看作是电。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_3": "这就像一条链条。这些点可以移动，但它们无法彼此分离。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_4": "电压源试图推动这一链条。它们试图从一侧推动，并向另一侧施加拉力。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_5": "要注意的是，点本身不代表能量，点的移动才代表电能。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_6": "这实际上是一个短路。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_7": "这里没有电阻，电压源能够快速移动这些点！",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_8": "将一个设备接入到电路里。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_9": "这些设备利用这些点的运动来获得能量。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.header": "连接线缆",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_1": "接线端子和线缆可用于传输电能。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_2": "要移除已连接的线缆，可使用空线轴。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_3": "绝缘电缆可以染色。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors_chunks.header": "在未加载的区块传输电力",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors_chunks.text_1": "在已加载的区块范围之外，电力仍能正常传输。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.header": "控制电流的方向",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_1": "这是一个好东西",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_2": "如果二极管的正极与电源正极相连，它将允许电流通过……",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_3": "....负极与电源负极相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_4": "这被称为单向导电性",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_5": "否则，电流将无法通过二极管",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_6": "反接的二极管将无法导电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.electric_train_sounds.header": "改变电气化列车的音效",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.electric_train_sounds.text_1": "电车在通电时会发出不一样的声音",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.electric_train_sounds.text_2": "加入某些方块可以改变声音的风格",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.header": "使用电能表",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_1": "电能表可以计量消耗的电能",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_2": "将电源正极连接到 “进线端子”",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_3": "将正极的 “负载端子”连接到用电器上",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_4": "最后，把回路接在 “零端子” 上",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_5": "电能表将开始计量流经它的电能",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.grounding.header": "大地也是导体",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.grounding.text_1": "大地亦可导电。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.header": "放置高压断路器",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_1": "高压断路器可以用来连接或断开高压电路",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_2": "要制作一个这样的装置，需要将一个连接器置于高压断路器的方向上",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_3": "在它们之间间隔一个方块的距离",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_4": "高压断路器可以手动操作……",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_5": "...也可以用红石控制",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.header": "列车电气化",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_1": "接触网支架会自动连接到附近的柱状物",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_2": "接触网可以为列车供电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_3": "要使用电力的列车需要有一个受电弓来与接触网接触……",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_4": "以及一个电动机……",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_5": "要给接触网供电，需要将接触网与电源正极相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_6": "将电源负极与接地棒相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_7": "2500 V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_8": "受电弓可以被染色",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.header": "使用继电器",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.text_1": "继电器本质上就是开关，只不过它是靠微弱的电流来驱动的",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.text_2": "将控制电路连接至“线圈”接线端子",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.text_3": "将被控电路连接至其余接线端",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.text_4": "扳动继电器，使其切换至常闭（NC）状态",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.resistance.header": "电阻对电路的影响",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.resistance.text_1": "如果没有电阻，灯泡会很亮",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.resistance.text_2": "1kΩ",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.resistance.text_3": "注意看，灯泡变暗了",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.resistance.text_4": "电阻限制了流过灯泡的电流",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.resistance.text_5": "坏处在于，这部分电能被白白浪费成了热量",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.shared.ratio1over2": "1 / 2",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.shared.ratio1over3": "1 / 3",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.shared.ratio3over1": "3 / 1",
