  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_4": "10A",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_5": "损失的电能与线缆的电阻值以及电流大小的平方成正比（W = RI²）。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_6": "变压器可用于提高电压，从而降低电流。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_7": "3.3A",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_8": "对于长途输电线路，加大电压可大大减少电能损失。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_turns.header": "变压器是如何工作的",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_turns.text_1": "变压器用于升高或降低电压",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_turns.text_2": "注意看，线圈的匝数比等于电压比",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_turns.text_3": "此外，变压器并不会将两个电路直接连通",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_turns.text_4": "相反，它是通过磁场来耦合这两个电路的",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.header": "什么是电压？",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_1": "电压是指电路中两点之间的电位差",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_10": "将一个设备接入电压差之间，电流便会开始流动并消耗能量来让用电器工作",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_11": "永远不要将不同电压直接相连！",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_12": "当两种不同的电压通过低电阻连接起来时，就会有大量的电流开始流动",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_2": "160V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_3": "70V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_4": "-160V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_5": "有时电压值可能仅表示一个特定点的数值。在这种情况下，该值是相对于地面而言的，而地面的电压始终为 0V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_6": "70V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_7": "230V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.voltage.text_8": "请注意，两个接线端子的的电压分别是 -160V 和 70V，但两者之间的电压差为 230V",
